body:
But who in the hell designed this monstrosity? I was just looking for a new mouse (coworker actually suggested a Logitech G600 and probably will get it) but while looking at options I found this eldritch horror of a peripheral.

https://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=9SIA9JN6093984&amp;cm_re=elecom_mouse-_-32K-004K-00001-_-Product

First of all, that&#039;s like 19 extra buttons on the mouse. Second of all, there&#039;s no rhyme or reason as to where they&#039;re placed. Look at that thing, &quot;We&#039;ll just slap 8 on one side, 3 on the other, 2 more underneath the palm and the rest wherever they can fit&quot;
